Title: 2017 WINTER CONFERENCE
Content:
The Leazer Group will be hosting their National Sales Conference at the beautiful Marriott at Crabtree in Raleigh, North Carolina! Mark your calendar on February 3rd & 4th for our biggest event of the year, our annual sales and inspiration conference! This event is designed to coach and train agents to help them  grow professionally and personally and becoming an agent of change.  From this event you will be given the tools to help increase your sales with product knowledge directly from the carriers, tips from all of our top producers, be coached and trained by the TLG leaders,  building an agency and most importantly associating with Art Leazer, Kimberly Narretto, Tom Brown and many more!

Success is not just for anyone, it’s for you! So come be part of the TLG experience and let 2017 be the year that you

“BREAKTHROUGH TO EXCELLENCE!”

Title: TLG Virtual Bootcamp
Content: Join TLG Founder & CEO, Art Leazer and VP of Sales & Marketing, Kimberly Narretto for LIVE Boot Camp training that be will streamed live from TLG HQ! Our Virtual Boot Camp is designed to help new & existing agents become proficient at our proprietary selling system. We will teach you how to make dials, book quality set appts, our exclusive in-home presentation and so much more! Registration is MANDATORY and attendance is LIMITED! Please see the link below for details!   After registering you will receive a confirmation email containing information about joining the training.   Please register for Virtual Boot Camp on Friday, June 9, 2017, 12:00 PM - 5:00 PM EDT at:  https://attendee.gototraining.com/r/7617574170416303617
